  displayName: Open Source Competitor
  description: A strong open-source model just dropped. It matches your capabilities
    for free.
  weight: 9
  conditions:
  - key: min_month
    value: 3
  choices:
  - id: differentiate
    text: Double down on proprietary features and UX
    description: -$2000, +5 Hype, -200 Users (some churn)
